Executive: Good morning.

Customer: To wo wo to WhatsApp chutti pe hai.
Executive: First first first baat karenge mujhe time kam hai main kahin pe hoon. Batao aap kya bolna hai aapko kya chahiye main.
Customer: Main sir do cheeze mujhe do cheeze aap se baat karni thi main Numan ki manager hoon. Actually first of all to aapka ek kaam karo main main ye number hai na aapka personal main kar raha hoon ab aapko.
Customer: Haan call kijiye kyunki sir aapki services hamper ho rahi hai.
